{
  "stem": "95.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, when I sang, I forgot where I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got involved with the song I was singing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think I made the other inmates kind of happy for that half-hour that I was doing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on top of it, the chef at the kitchen will give me a piece of bread and a soup extra.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always say that you could not survive alone in camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you were alone, you could not do it by yourself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to have members of your family that you love and stick together, or you had to have friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother-in-law, unfortunately-- and it's again, my youth, and I'm putting the blame on me for what I did-- he said-- well, because he lost his two son-- hold me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I am his son now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was my brother-in-law, you know, not somebody that I knew quite well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why should he tell me what to do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somehow, we did not manage to get along quite well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were separated, though-- though he stayed in the camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw him, I saw him, but we were not holding each other to dear life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe if I-- maybe if it was my brother, it would have been different.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I got involved with two young French kids, and they were magnificent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "George and-- I can't even think of the other name, but it'll come to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, they-- they were-- we would stick together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would share everything we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We would talk about our past in France, and-- and it was just marvelous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that helps you, because if you feel low one day, if the other person boost you up, then the general morale will just go back.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
